msgid "Wait a moment."
msgstr "ちょっと待って。"

msgid "This doesn't look right. We should've come across stairs a while back."
msgstr "おかしいわ。もう随分前に、階段に着いてないといけないはず。"

msgid "That's true."
msgstr "そうね。"

msgid "Maybe we took a wrong turn somewhere...?"
msgstr "どこかで道を間違えたのかしら……？"

msgid "Let's just keep going."
msgstr "とにかく、先に進みましょう。"

msgid "I want to see what's on the other side of this hallway."
msgstr "廊下の反対側に何があるか見ておきたい。"
